giftcurs (0.5.3-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Layout is determined by configurable formatting strings.
  * Better support for viewing important messages from giFT.
  * Support for Tru64 (OSF1 V4.0) and OSF1 curses.
  * Various bug fixes.

